## Get home page

GET http://localhost:3232/
Accept-Charset: utf-8

## Fetch 10 cocktails from the feed, in transit-json

POST http://localhost:3232/bartender/cocktails/feed?cocktails=10
Accept-Charset: utf-8
Accept: application/transit+json

## Do a fulltext search, expect some t+j back

POST http://localhost:3232/bartender/cocktails/fulltext?search=negroni
Accept-Charset: utf-8
Accept: application/transit+json

